OL,3,CPlans unveiled for multi-million-pound
OL,4,Cwater treatment plant
OL,6,FPlans are being developed for a new
OL,7,Fmulti-million-pound water treatment
OL,8,Fworks in Dumfries and Galloway.
OL,10,FScottish Water says the new works near
OL,11,FBoreland will ensure it can "continue
OL,12,Fto provide clear, fresh, high-quality
OL,13,Fdrinking water to 40,000 households
OL,14,Fand businesses in Lockerbie, Annan,
OL,15,FDumfries and the surrounding area, now
OL,16,Fand in the future".
