OL,3,CPlans unveiled for multi-million-pound
OL,4,Cwater treatment plant
OL,6,FThe existing Black Esk Water Treatment
OL,7,FWorks was built in the mid-eighties
OL,8,Fand supplies up to 21.6 million litres
OL,9,Fof water each day, the equivalent of
OL,10,Fnearly nine Olympic-sized swimming
OL,11,Fpools.
OL,13,FScottish Water said the site would
OL,14,F"utilise innovative, new water
OL,15,Ftreatment technologies" and would be
OL,16,F"built by specialist teams in Scotland
OL,17,Fusing some offsite construction
OL,18,Ftechniques to cut construction times,
OL,19,Fdisruption, and carbon".
