OL,3,CPlans unveiled for multi-million-pound
OL,4,Cwater treatment plant
OL,6,FThe new works will be located on land
OL,7,Fadjacent to the existing works, within
OL,8,Fan area of commercial woodland.
OL,10,FIt will be supplied by raw water from
OL,11,FBlack Esk reservoir through existing
OL,12,Fpipework and infrastructure.
OL,14,FStewart Smolarek, Scottish Water's
OL,15,FProject Manager said: "The new works
OL,16,Fwill use the latest state-of-the-art
OL,17,Fceramic membrane treatment to provide
OL,18,Fhigh-quality, fresh drinking water
OL,19,Fthat meets the needs of present and
OL,20,Ffuture generations.
