OL,3,CPlans unveiled for multi-million-pound
OL,4,Cwater treatment plant
OL,6,F"An advantage of this type of
OL,7,Ftechnology is the ability to build
OL,8,Fparts of the kit off-site to reduce
OL,9,Fthe amount of onsite construction, it
OL,10,Ftakes less time to build and cuts
OL,11,Fcarbon costs.
OL,13,F"We will also be looking to include
OL,14,Frenewable energy sources at the site
OL,15,Fand to offset the delivery of energy
OL,16,Fused to help Scottish Water reach its
OL,17,Fambitious zero carbon target."
