OL,3,CPlans unveiled for multi-million-pound
OL,4,Cwater treatment plant
OL,6,FScott Fraser, Corporate Affairs
OL,7,FManager at Scottish Water said: "We
OL,8,Fare now starting the detailed design
OL,9,Fprocess and have engaged with those
OL,10,Fliving closest to help us gather local
OL,11,Fknowledge and feedback before any
OL,12,Fplanning applications are submitted.
OL,14,F"Through this engagement, we have
OL,15,Fbegun the process of reviewing the
OL,16,Fsize and layout of the new building
OL,17,Fand are reviewing the potential site
OL,18,Fentrance.
