OL,6,F"Our priority is to minimise
OL,7,Fdisruption and work with local
OL,8,Fresidents and the community throughout
OL,9,Fthe development and delivery of this
OL,10,Fproject."
OL,12,FPreparatory felling on the commercial
OL,13,Fwoodland started in February to
OL,14,Funderstand the ground conditions.
OL,16,FAs compensatory planting, Scottish
OL,17,FWater has committed to planting nearly
OL,18,F3,200 broadleaved trees at Ettrick,
OL,19,Fabout 20 miles away, by the end of
OL,20,FMarch.
